Sandalodesmini 
<bibRefCitation author="Hoffman, R. L." box="[433,619,1544,1570]" pageId="1" pageNumber="261" pagination="247 - 259" refId="ref5695" refString="Hoffman, R. L. (1982) Chelodesmid studies. XVIII. A synopsis of the genus Sandalodesmus Silvestri, 1902, and proposal of the new tribe Sandalodesmini (Polydesmida: Chelodesmidae). Spixiana, 5 (3), 247 - 259. https: // www. biodiversitylibrary. org / page / 28194567" type="journal article" year="1982">Hoffman, 1982</bibRefCitation>
